{"type": "article", "id": 62424, "title": "天猫新广告鼓励跟风，麦当劳用模糊照片展示经典产品 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人的一切", "date": "2019-03-27T05:07:57Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 417, "name": "趋势"}, {"id": 57510, "name": "纪念瓶"}, {"id": 3263, "name": "Loewe"}, {"id": 1329, "name": "天猫"}, {"id": 332, "name": "百威"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 1480589, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 36, "image": "img/article/article_show/20190327124304QXvB9KZyhRx6C4Wl.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">明星又代言了啥</h3><p line=\"wlSv\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4354073946066344?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Olay 宣布阿云嘎和郑云龙成为全新品牌大使，</b></a>并且在天猫超级品牌日活动期间组成“美白组合”，宣传升级后的美白产品。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190327124345qHWzj9IYPUyLTfQx.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.630952\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"hm89\" class=\"\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4354062285612117?\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Loewe 昨天推出《Z.TAO, Me and Myself 2019》画册，由黄子韬和他的蜡像共同来演绎品牌 2019 春夏男装系列。</b></a>限量 1000 册发售。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190327124412hyNHRUWLSgmpnTaX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.295370\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190327124427R8D4iohmJgZe1XwB.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.968354\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><h3>值得一看的 Case</h3><p line=\"UVtG\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4353881322481697?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>天猫昨天推出一支“跟风无罪”的主题广告片。</b></a>片中展现了复古摩登风、户外机能风、美式滑板风等 9 个春夏流行趋势，并传递跟风不是问题，消费者顺应内心的选择，找到适合自己的风格。广告拍得不错。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=s0854w9phx5\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"92vQ\"><a href=\"https://youtu.be/KBvNSznpg0s\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>百威和杰基·罗宾森基因会合作，为纪念美国第一位非裔棒球运动员杰基·罗宾森诞生 100 周年，推出一系列 “Impact” campaign。</b></a>这其中包括一支由 Spike Lee 拍摄的纪念短片，片中请来杰基·罗宾森女儿讲述父亲的经历。此外，百威还发布了主题海报和定制瓶身。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=b0854blqbh0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190327124719TUCmBLqwtOGh1a0b.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.441921\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190327124720wCgOPu8tDFTZWcLn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.441434\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190327124721xr2WD7lnh4FImHRu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.442187\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190327124720XFJpxOmUSKzTi31L.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.443067\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190327124722pd4TIXbJuvhfK9yA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.441921\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190327124720wAaGLsthREfOICzy.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"3.528037\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190327124721zgdbEaH3Qv2MsGK5.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"3.528037\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"XAzM\"><a href=\"https://www.adweek.com/brand-marketing/mcdonalds-and-tbwas-blurry-big-mac-billboards-are-totally-ingenious/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>麦当劳户外广告中展示了变模糊的经典产品。</b></a>广告上唯一的广告词“不必再说”表达了巨无霸、薯条这些产品外形深入人心，即使模糊人们也能认出来。创意代理商是 TBWA/San Juan.</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190327124836JiVs1C3DxnhKwlSb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561798\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201903271248365Tx0y38k9AMtGvCc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2019032712483663ny7Ex0GcejUfKt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561798\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"DMxD\"><a href=\"https://justaddspotify.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Spotify 澳大利亚推出一个 “justaddspotify.com” 的网站。</b></a>它在网站首页上罗列了一些人们经常搜索的问题，点开之后便是对应的简短解释和推荐歌单。这些活动主要是针对 30-45 岁的中年人，他们经常使用网络却没什么时间搜索答案。里面除了歌单还有播客、新闻等 Spotify 近期主推的新功能。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190327124851JTSIoevtyR29dwFK.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.404647\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190327124851B8PTu5p2ICRh9fXK.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.411195\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190327124851D91ybjMFtPknxhm0.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.540193\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"QeMw\"><b><a href=\"https://youtu.be/mB71Sktk0bQ\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">连锁三明治 Jimmy John‘s 最近发布了系列广告</a>，</b>来宣传它只在位置 5 公里范围内提供配送服务，以此来保证食物的新鲜度。例如一位富翁以为自己拥有了一切，而发现自己住在配送距离以外，颇感遗憾。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=r0854ni4yvm\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=l0854jd52xl\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=c0854038m0l\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><h3>其他，也很重要</h3><p line=\"UcmO\"><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/articles/118985.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\" rel=\"nofollow\">克劳锐发布了《 2019 中国 MCN 行业发展研究白皮书》。</a>报告提到，截止 2018 年 12 月，国内已经有超过 5000 家 MCN 公司，90% 的网红签约公司或者成立了自己的公司。这些公司可以粗略分为电商型、泛内容型、营销型和知识型，泛内容型和营销型对平台依赖属性更强。</p><p line=\"Yula\">头部 MCN 集中于北上广深一线城市，他们取得的收益占到整个市场的 60%。业态形式基本是围绕内容生产和运营协助账号变现。</p><p line=\"Yula\" class=\"\"><br></p><p line=\"F9Fp\">题图来自：&nbsp;<a href=\"https://unsplash.com/photos/LsfqHXdAvfk?utm_source=unsplash&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_content=creditCopyText\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Priscilla Du Preez</a> on <a href=\"https://unsplash.com/search/photos/fashion-cool?utm_source=unsplash&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_content=creditCopyText\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Unsplash</a></p>"}